	(text "| Pin | Default | Description |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| IO5 | Pull-up | Voltage level of IO5 and IO15 affects the timing of SDIO Slave. |\n| IO0 | Pull-up | Pull LOW to enter download mode. |\n| IO2 | Pull-down | IO0 and IO2 together will make ESP32 enter download mode. |\n| IO12 (MTDI) | Pull-down | Pull HIGH and ESP32 will fail to boot normally. |\n| IO15 (MTDO) | Pull-up | Pull LOW to disable debug log output. Voltage level of IO5 and IO15 affects SDIO Slave timing. |"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 123.19 36.068 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
